A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Hospitals and Tissue Banks – Autologous and Directed Blood Donations –
3 Requirements
4 FOR the purpose of requiring a tissue bank that facilitates autologous or directed blood
5 donations to comply with a physician’s order prescribing an autologous or directed
6 blood donation; authorizing a tissue bank to charge a certain fee for facilitating an
7 autologous or directed blood donation; requiring a hospital to allow an individual to
8 provide an autologous or directed blood donation under certain circumstances; and
9 generally relating to autologous and directed blood donations.
